# Requirements Quality Checklist: Widget-Based Dashboard Framework

**Purpose**: Validate specification quality, completeness, and clarity as "unit tests for English"
**Created**: 2025-10-11
**Feature**: [spec.md](../spec.md)
**Checklist Type**: Requirements Quality Validation

## Requirement Completeness

### Core Widget System Requirements

- [ ] **CHK001** - Are widget refresh behaviors clearly specified for all network conditions (online, offline, slow connection)? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK002** - Are widget error recovery mechanisms defined (retry logic, fallback data, user notification)? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK003** - Are loading state requirements consistent across all 5 widget types? [Consistency, Spec §FR-003]
- [ ] **CHK004** - Are widget lifecycle requirements documented (mount, update, unmount, cleanup)? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK005** - Are requirements defined for widget dependency management when one widget's output feeds another? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK006** - Are widget state persistence requirements specified (survive page refresh, navigation)? [Gap]

### Data & Calculation Requirements

- [ ] **CHK007** - Are calculation error handling requirements defined for invalid data types? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK008** - Are requirements specified for calculation performance with large datasets (>50K records)? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK009** - Is the calculation pipeline ordering requirement testable when multiple operations apply? [Measurability, Spec §FR-010]
- [ ] **CHK010** - Are data transformation requirements defined for type conversions (string→number, date parsing)? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK011** - Are requirements specified for handling null, undefined, or missing values in calculations? [Edge Case, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK012** - Are calculation result caching requirements defined to avoid redundant computation? [Gap]

### Dashboard Management Requirements

- [ ] **CHK013** - Are dashboard naming requirements specified (length limits, character restrictions, uniqueness)? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK014** - Are requirements defined for dashboard deletion safeguards (confirmation, undo, recovery)? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK015** - Are dashboard versioning requirements specified for tracking changes over time? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK016** - Are requirements defined for dashboard import/export functionality? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK017** - Are dashboard sharing permission requirements clearly specified? [Ambiguity, Spec §FR-034]
- [ ] **CHK018** - Are conflict resolution requirements defined when dashboard configurations diverge across devices? [Gap]

### Layout & Positioning Requirements

- [ ] **CHK019** - Are minimum and maximum widget dimensions quantified with specific pixel/grid values? [Clarity, Spec §FR-020]
- [ ] **CHK020** - Are collision detection requirements testable with specific overlap tolerance thresholds? [Measurability, Spec §FR-021]
- [ ] **CHK021** - Are responsive layout breakpoint values explicitly specified? [Clarity, Spec §FR-022]
- [ ] **CHK022** - Are requirements defined for layout behavior during window resize/orientation change? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK023** - Are z-index/stacking requirements specified when widgets overlap during animation? [Edge Case, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK024** - Are requirements defined for widget positioning on ultra-wide (>3840px) displays? [Edge Case, Spec §FR-022]

### API Integration Requirements

- [ ] **CHK025** - Are API metadata refresh requirements specified (how often, automatic vs manual)? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK026** - Are requirements defined for handling API endpoint deprecation/removal? [Exception Flow, Spec §Edge Cases]
- [ ] **CHK027** - Are API authentication requirements consistent with existing system auth? [Consistency, Spec §Assumptions]
- [ ] **CHK028** - Are requirements specified for API response pagination handling? [Gap]
- [ ] **CHK029** - Are API timeout requirements quantified with specific millisecond values? [Clarity, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK030** - Are requirements defined for API response schema validation? [Gap]

## Requirement Clarity

### Ambiguous Terms & Definitions

- [ ] **CHK031** - Is "self-contained widget" precisely defined with specific isolation criteria? [Ambiguity, Spec §FR-002]
- [ ] **CHK032** - Is "user-friendly error message" quantified with specific content requirements? [Ambiguity, Spec §Edge Cases]
- [ ] **CHK033** - Is "automatically adjusts positions" defined with specific repositioning algorithm? [Ambiguity, Spec §FR-021]
- [ ] **CHK034** - Is "gracefully handle rate limiting" specified with concrete retry behavior? [Ambiguity, Spec §FR-027]
- [ ] **CHK035** - Is "real-time preview" quantified with acceptable latency threshold? [Clarity, Spec §FR-031]
- [ ] **CHK036** - Is "global filters" scope clearly defined (which widgets respect them, inheritance rules)? [Ambiguity, Spec §FR-018]

### Measurability Issues

- [ ] **CHK037** - Can "smooth" widget resize be objectively measured with frame rate requirements? [Measurability, Spec §User Story 4]
- [ ] **CHK038** - Can "balanced visual weight" acceptance criteria be verified? [Measurability, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK039** - Can "helpful status messages" be objectively evaluated? [Measurability, Spec §User Story 1]
- [ ] **CHK040** - Can "prominent" positioning be measured with specific coordinate/size requirements? [Measurability, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK041** - Can "appropriate formatting" be validated with specific format specifications? [Measurability, Spec §FR-011]

## Requirement Consistency

### Cross-Requirement Alignment

- [ ] **CHK042** - Are auto-refresh intervals consistent between FR-004 (30-60 min) and User Story 1 (60 sec)? [Conflict, Spec §FR-004]
- [ ] **CHK043** - Are widget count limits consistent across requirements (FR-008: 50, SC-008: 50)? [Consistency]
- [ ] **CHK044** - Are performance requirements aligned between SC-004 (2 sec) and SC-005 (3 sec)? [Consistency]
- [ ] **CHK045** - Are data format requirements consistent (JSON mentioned in Assumptions but not FR-026)? [Consistency]
- [ ] **CHK046** - Are permission requirements consistent between FR-033 and FR-034? [Consistency]

### Template vs Custom Dashboard Consistency

- [ ] **CHK047** - Are requirements consistent for pre-built templates and custom dashboards? [Consistency, Spec §FR-016]
- [ ] **CHK048** - Do template customization requirements align with widget configuration requirements? [Consistency]
- [ ] **CHK049** - Are template data source requirements consistent with FR-002 widget independence? [Consistency]

## Acceptance Criteria Quality

### Success Criteria Measurability

- [ ] **CHK050** - Is SC-001 "5 minutes" measured from which starting point (blank dashboard, template, logged in)? [Clarity, Spec §SC-001]
- [ ] **CHK051** - Is SC-003 "90% of users" sample size and measurement methodology defined? [Measurability, Spec §SC-003]
- [ ] **CHK052** - Is SC-006 "performance degradation" quantified with specific threshold metrics? [Ambiguity, Spec §SC-006]
- [ ] **CHK053** - Is SC-009 "60% of active users" definition of "active user" specified? [Ambiguity, Spec §SC-009]
- [ ] **CHK054** - Is SC-016 "10 minutes saved per day" measurement methodology defined? [Measurability, Spec §SC-016]
- [ ] **CHK055** - Is SC-017 "fewer than 5 bugs per 100 users" severity classification specified? [Clarity, Spec §SC-017]

### User Story Acceptance Scenarios

- [ ] **CHK056** - Are User Story 1 acceptance scenarios independently testable without dependencies? [Testability]
- [ ] **CHK057** - Are User Story 3 "preview" acceptance criteria quantified with specific data display requirements? [Measurability, Spec §User Story 3]
- [ ] **CHK058** - Are User Story 4 layout persistence acceptance criteria verifiable across browser sessions? [Testability]
- [ ] **CHK059** - Are User Story 5 calculation acceptance criteria mathematically verifiable? [Measurability]

## Scenario Coverage

### Primary Flow Coverage

- [ ] **CHK060** - Are requirements complete for the first-time user experience creating their first dashboard? [Coverage, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK061** - Are requirements specified for dashboard duplication/cloning workflow? [Coverage, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK062** - Are requirements defined for widget reordering within the same dashboard? [Coverage, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK063** - Are requirements specified for dashboard filtering (search, sort, categorize saved dashboards)? [Coverage, Gap]

### Alternate Flow Coverage

- [ ] **CHK064** - Are requirements defined for keyboard-only dashboard creation and editing? [Coverage, Accessibility, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK065** - Are requirements specified for mobile touch interaction with drag-drop layout? [Coverage, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK066** - Are requirements defined for dashboard creation from existing widget configurations? [Coverage, Gap]

### Exception Flow Coverage

- [ ] **CHK067** - Are requirements specified for widget configuration validation failures? [Exception Flow, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK068** - Are requirements defined for dashboard save failures (network, storage limits)? [Exception Flow, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK069** - Are requirements specified for invalid API metadata responses? [Exception Flow, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK070** - Are requirements defined for circular dependency detection in widget calculations? [Exception Flow, Gap]

### Recovery Flow Coverage

- [ ] **CHK071** - Are dashboard autosave/recovery requirements specified for unsaved changes? [Recovery, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK072** - Are requirements defined for restoring accidentally deleted dashboards? [Recovery, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK073** - Are requirements specified for recovering from widget data fetch timeouts? [Recovery, Spec §Edge Cases]
- [ ] **CHK074** - Are requirements defined for dashboard state recovery after browser crash? [Recovery, Gap]

## Edge Case Coverage

### Data Boundary Cases

- [ ] **CHK075** - Are requirements specified for widgets with zero data results? [Edge Case, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK076** - Are requirements defined for extremely small datasets (1-2 records)? [Edge Case, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK077** - Are requirements specified for data with extreme values (very large/small numbers)? [Edge Case, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK078** - Are requirements defined for date range calculations spanning years/decades? [Edge Case, Gap]

### UI Boundary Cases

- [ ] **CHK079** - Are requirements specified for dashboards with only 1 widget? [Edge Case, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK080** - Are requirements defined for dashboards at maximum widget limit (50 widgets)? [Edge Case, Spec §FR-008]
- [ ] **CHK081** - Are requirements specified for widget titles exceeding display width? [Edge Case, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK082** - Are requirements defined for dashboards viewed on minimum supported screen size (320px)? [Edge Case, Spec §FR-022]

### Timing Edge Cases

- [ ] **CHK083** - Are requirements specified for widgets refreshing during active user editing? [Edge Case, Spec §Edge Cases]
- [ ] **CHK084** - Are requirements defined for rapid dashboard switching (< 1 second intervals)? [Edge Case, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK085** - Are requirements specified for simultaneous multi-widget data fetch (race conditions)? [Edge Case, Gap]

### State Edge Cases

- [ ] **CHK086** - Are requirements defined for dashboard behavior when user session expires mid-edit? [Edge Case, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK087** - Are requirements specified for widget behavior when API endpoint becomes unavailable? [Edge Case, Spec §Edge Cases]
- [ ] **CHK088** - Are requirements defined for dashboard behavior during system maintenance windows? [Edge Case, Gap]

## Non-Functional Requirements

### Performance Requirements

- [ ] **CHK089** - Are memory consumption limits specified for dashboards with 50 widgets? [NFR, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK090** - Are CPU usage requirements defined during widget calculation execution? [NFR, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK091** - Are network bandwidth requirements specified for multi-widget data fetching? [NFR, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK092** - Are requirements defined for graceful degradation under resource constraints? [NFR, Gap]

### Security Requirements

- [ ] **CHK093** - Are XSS prevention requirements specified for user-generated dashboard names? [Security, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK094** - Are CSRF protection requirements defined for dashboard save operations? [Security, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK095** - Are input validation requirements specified for widget configuration parameters? [Security, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK096** - Are requirements defined for sanitizing API response data before display? [Security, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK097** - Are SQL injection prevention requirements specified for calculation filters? [Security, Gap]

### Accessibility Requirements

- [ ] **CHK098** - Are WCAG 2.1 AA compliance requirements specified for all dashboard UI elements? [Accessibility, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK099** - Are keyboard navigation requirements defined for all dashboard builder interactions? [Accessibility, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK100** - Are screen reader requirements specified for widget data announcements? [Accessibility, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK101** - Are focus management requirements defined for modal dialogs and drag operations? [Accessibility, Gap]
- [ ] **CHK102** - Are color contrast requirements specified for widget visual states? [Accessibility, Gap]

### Usability Requirements

